@Everyone complaining at the Jinx ult nerf: /laugh

You guys seriously...
that was one of the most broken ults in the game. It still deals the SAME DAMAGE, UNLESS YOU HIT IT POINT BLANK. That's right! If you actually use some of that brainpower you possess, you would realize it's an incredibly healthy change, that forces Jinx players to put thought and reasoning into pressing R.
